    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. The S65 4.0L V8 remains in peak mechanical health, delivering an uncompromising 8,400 RPM redline with perfect compression across all cylinders. Paired with a precision-calibrated M-DCT dual-clutch gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, the drivetrain offers immediate throttle response and seamless power transfer. The chassis maintains its original rigidity, free of fatigue, and the suspension geometry is dialed to factory tolerances. This is a collector-grade example with impeccable provenance and zero deferred maintenance.",
